extends /sites/ChickenGame/layouts/base.pug

block variables
    - const title = 'Privacy Policy | Chicken Game'
    - const description = 'Read the Privacy Policy for Chicken Game, where we ensure your privacy and protect your personal information while you enjoy playing the game directly on our platform. Learn how we collect, use, and safeguard your data.'

block content
    +Header()

    main
        section.container.privacy-policy
            h1 Privacy Policy for Chicken Game
            p At Chicken Game, we prioritize the privacy and security of our players. We are committed to safeguarding your personal information and providing a safe, enjoyable experience. This Privacy Policy outlines the data we collect, how we use it, and how we protect your privacy while you play the game directly on our website. If you have any questions or need more details about this policy, please feel free to contact us.

            h2 Information We Collect
            p While you play Chicken Game on our website, we collect certain details that help us enhance your overall experience. This includes data such as your IP address, browser type, and the device you use to access the platform. We also track in-game interactions, including team selections, gameplay activities, and other interactions within the platform. This information is used to improve your experience and is not linked to personally identifiable data.

            h2 Log Files
            p Chicken Game employs log files to monitor and analyze activity on our platform. This includes details like your IP address, browser type, Internet Service Provider (ISP), timestamp, pages visited, and interactions within the app. This data is used solely for analytics, site performance, and general demographic analysis. It is not linked to any personally identifiable information.

            h2 Third-Party Services
            p To improve the performance and features of Chicken Game, we may collaborate with third-party services to enhance website and app analytics, as well as improve gameplay experience. These third-party services may gather anonymous data to understand user behavior better but will not collect any personally identifiable information.

            h2 Advertising Partners
            p Some of our advertising partners may collect data to display relevant ads to users. Each of these partners operates with its own privacy policy, and we encourage you to review their privacy terms before engaging with their content.

            h2 Privacy Policies of Advertising Partners
            p While we collaborate with advertising partners, Chicken Game is not responsible for the data collection practices of these external parties. We recommend you read their privacy policies and manage your preferences accordingly.

            h2 Data Security
            p We implement standard security measures to protect the data we collect and prevent unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. While we strive to maintain a secure environment, please note that no method of data transmission over the internet is entirely foolproof. We continuously work to enhance our security practices to ensure your information remains safe.

            h2 User Rights
            p You have the right to access, modify, or request the deletion of any personal data we may have collected. If you wish to exercise these rights or have questions regarding your data, please reach out to our support team for assistance.

            h2 Children's Privacy
            p At Chicken Game, we take children's privacy seriously. We strongly advise parents and guardians to supervise their children's online activities. Chicken Game does not knowingly collect or store personal information from users under the age of 18. If you believe your child has shared such information with us, please contact us immediately, and we will take the necessary actions to remove this data.

            h2 Data Retention
            p We retain user data only for as long as it is necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy. Once data is no longer needed for analytics or platform improvements, it is securely deleted or anonymized.

            h2 Online Privacy Only
            p This Privacy Policy applies exclusively to online activities and pertains to users who visit ChickenGame.com. It does not cover any information collected offline or through other means outside the website or app.

            h2 Updates to This Privacy Policy
            p We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in legal regulations or platform features. We encourage users to review this page periodically to stay informed about how we protect your information.

            h2 Consent
            p By using our website and playing Chicken Game directly on the platform, you consent to this Privacy Policy and agree to its terms. If you have any questions or concerns, don't hesitate to contact our team.

            p If you have any additional questions or require further clarification on how we manage your data, feel free to reach out to us at any time.


    +Footer()